Package org.elasticsearch.xpack.ql.expression.gen.pipeline

Class Pipe

java.lang.Object
org.elasticsearch.xpack.ql.tree.Node<Pipe>
org.elasticsearch.xpack.ql.expression.gen.pipeline.Pipe
All Implemented Interfaces:
Resolvable, FieldExtraction
Direct Known Subclasses:
BinaryOptionalMathPipe, BinaryPipe, InsertFunctionPipe, LeafInput, LocateFunctionPipe, MultiPipe, ReplaceFunctionPipe, ScorePipe, StartsWithFunctionPipe, SubstringFunctionPipe, ThreeArgsDateTimePipe, UnaryPipe
public abstract class Pipe extends Node<Pipe> implements FieldExtraction, Resolvable
Processing pipe for an expression (tree). Used for local execution of expressions on the invoking node. For example, the Pipe of: ABS(MAX(foo)) + CAST(bar) Is an Add operator with left ABS over an aggregate (MAX), and right being a CAST function.
